				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">use this song for lulling<a name="12760"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 3 03 11:22 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>It seems to me that this song is VERY useful.  On many a LDoN mission I've been called upon for lulling a room, this will make it easier indeed.  I can lull through closed doors, I can lull things that I can't see, but I CAN'T lull things that I cannot target, so with this song I will be able to target those mobs hiding just on the inside of the door waiting to pounce upon me should I physically try to peek around the corner.  I'm buying it today.</span></td>
