				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: use this song for lulling<a name="12945"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Dec 8 03 8:12 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I've done about 15 levels with my bard in LDoN dungeons, and I'd like to think I've become a very good puller.  However, I find most groups refuse to allow the puller the luxury of cautious pulls and little tricks such as what you suggest.
<br />

<br />
I find that opening doors from as far away as possible and lulling any I can see first usually does the trick.  If it doesn't, I always have a mezz handy.
<br />

<br />
Calliopee
<br />
E'ci</span></td>
